body.description: The perfect first aid kit for cars, homes, and job sites, this 25-person kit prepares you for tackling minor emergencies. This 106-piece compact first aid kit has supplies for treating pain and swelling, as well as cuts, scrapes, and wounds. This small first aid kit comes in an easy-to-carry metal case with easy-to-release latches designed to ensure quick first aid access in the event of an emergency. Our first aid kits for businesses, home renovation projects, and construction vehicles allow you to treat minor cuts and scrapes just about anywhere.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 10, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good product, not enough protection for shipment in packaging.
reviews.reviewText: My shipment was damaged also. There is just not enough packaging around the cabinet for shipping. The problem report process said no refunds. Not the products fault. So other than that, this seems like a great product. Not large quantities for what you pay, but a good value in this product is the Smartcompliance system. Most of the items boxes fit snuggly into a plastic frame which prevents users from taking things out and not putting them back where they should be. The take one boxes have a reorder card in it to prompt you to reorder. Together this will hopefully lead to a well organized and well stocked cabinet for years to come instead of a ransacked mostly empty and cluttered cabinet six months from now. The cabinet is good size and will allow for the stocking of a few other items such as meds, etc.
